{"metadata":{"modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"role":"symbol","externalID":"c:@E@MLNTextWritingMode@MLNTextWritingModeVertical","symbolKind":"case","roleHeading":"Enumeration Case","title":"MLNTextWritingModeVertical","fragments":[{"text":"MLNTextWritingModeVertical","kind":"identifier"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"MLNTextWritingModeVertical","kind":"identifier"}]},"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlntextwritingmode\/mlntextwritingmodevertical"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"kind":"symbol","identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"occ","url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNTextWritingMode\/MLNTextWritingModeVertical"},"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"patch":0,"minor":3},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNTextWritingMode"]]},"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"MLNTextWritingModeVertical","kind":"identifier"}],"languages":["occ"],"platforms":["iOS"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"content":[{"anchor":"discussion","level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Discussion"},{"code":[" If a text's language supports vertical writing mode, symbols with point"," placement would be laid out vertically."],"syntax":null,"type":"codeListing"}],"kind":"content"}],"sections":[],"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNTextWritingMode":{"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlntextwritingmode","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNTextWritingMode"}],"title":"MLNTextWritingMode","kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNTextWritingMode","abstract":[{"text":"The property allows control over a symbol’s orientation. Note that the property","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"values act as a hint, so that a symbol whose language doesn’t support the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"provided orientation will be laid out in its natural orientation. Example:","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"English point symbol will be rendered horizontally even if array value contains","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"single ‘vertical’ enum value. The order of elements in an array define priority","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"order for the placement of an orientation variant.","type":"text"}],"role":"symbol","type":"topic"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNTextWritingMode/MLNTextWritingModeVertical":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNTextWritingMode\/MLNTextWritingModeVertical","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlntextwritingmode\/mlntextwritingmodevertical","abstract":[],"fragments":[{"text":"MLNTextWritingModeVertical","kind":"identifier"}],"kind":"symbol","title":"MLNTextWritingModeVertical","role":"symbol","type":"topic"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre","title":"MapLibre","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control over data sources and styling."}],"type":"topic","role":"collection"}}}